                     </did>
                     <odd id="aspace_3999449825d81a0d1a29544faf6959a0">
                        <head>General</head>
                        <p>In this letter Taggart expresses his fears that the President is leading the nation toward a needless war with Great Britain. Taggart suspects clandestine dealings between Washington and Paris.</p>
                     </odd>
                  </c>
