               <scopecontent id="aspace_cadca85123728a26cdddefb00b22c3c3">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>These journals contain little more than a daily account of the weather, deaths, and visits to friends. There is one description of the military developments in the French-Indian War for the month of July, 1759. In the diary for 1812 Forward mentions Bonaparte's march on Europe.</p>
               </scopecontent>
